query: SELECT e.id, e.firstName, e.lastName, COUNT(te.id) as timeEntriesCount FROM employees e LEFT JOIN employeeProjectAssignments epa ON e.id = epa.employeeId LEFT JOIN timeEntries te ON epa.id = te.assignmentId GROUP BY e.id ORDER BY e.id DESC LIMIT 15
